journal.title: First Morning Win
journal.content: Tried the new morning routine today. Didn’t check my phone right away and instead sat outside for 10 minutes with coffee. It felt surprisingly calming. I think I want to try stretching next time. Small step, but felt good.

journal.title: Unexpected Benefit
journal.content: It’s only been a few days, but I’ve noticed I’m less anxious in the mornings. Not being bombarded by notifications immediately helps a lot. Also gives me time to breathe before the day starts. Didn’t expect such a quick shift.
